  <bpmn:process id="ComplaintOverview" name="ComplaintOrchestration" isExecutable="true">
    <bpmn:documentation>OVERVIEW diagram - all 5 stages. The 3 automated stages are COLLAPSED SUBPROCESSES (click the [+] to drill into the internal steps); they mirror the executable trigger-started files IntakeProcess.bpmn / InvestigationProcess.bpmn / CapaProcess.bpmn, which are the real runtime (each started by its own Data Fabric trigger). Triage is human-only in the tracker app. Every stage transition is a human advancing the Gate field; each advance fires a Data Fabric event trigger.</bpmn:documentation>
    <bpmn:extensionElements>
      <uipath:variables version="v1">
        <uipath:inputOutput id="complaintId" name="ComplaintID" type="string" elementId="ComplaintOverview" default="=js:&#34;CMP&#34; + new Date().toISOString().slice(0, 19).replace(/[-T:]/g, &#34;&#34;)" custom="true" />
        <uipath:inputOutput id="error14" name="Error" type="jsonSchema" elementId="Activity_okLY9r"><![CDATA[{"type":"object","properties":{"code":{"type":"string"},"message":{"type":"string"},"detail":{"type":"string"},"category":{"type":"string"},"status":{"type":"number"},"element":{"type":"string"}}}]]></uipath:inputOutput>
