    <bpmn:subProcess id="SubProcess_Intake" name="INTAKE">
      <bpmn:documentation>Stage 1 - mirrors IntakeProcess.bpmn (manual start). Fetch newest unread email -&gt; Extract agent -&gt; create Data Fabric record at Gate=Triage.</bpmn:documentation>
